[{"Id": 1015828, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "It is recommended to perform bath before wearing the Ehraam with an intention of wearing Ehraam. It is better to wear Ehraam after obligatory prayer. Shaikh Sudooq says, ’Recite dua <Allahummaj A’l-ho Lee Nooran> while performing Ghusl-e-Ehraam.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustahab hai keh Libaas-e-Ehraam se pehle ehraam ki niyyat se ghusl kare aur behtar hai keh waajib namaz adaa karne ke baad haalat-e-ehraam mein aaye. Shaikh Sadooq ne farmaya hai keh ehraam ke ghusl ke waqt dua <Allahummaj A’l-ho Lee Nooran> ka padhna mustahab hai.", "UrduDescription": "مستحب ہے کہ لباس احرام سے پہلے احرام کی نیت سے غسل کرے اور بہتر ہے کہ واجب نماز ادا کرنے کے بعد حالت احرام میں آئے۔ شیخ صدوق نے فرمایا ہے کہ احرام کے غسل کے وقت دُعا <اَللّٰہُمَّ اجْعَلْہُ لِیْ نُوْرًا> کا پڑھنا مستحب ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueS